message.body: Hi Monica!! :-) I have a signal and thought of you! Roo roo!
Mrow mrow! Want to talk for a minute?
Will you be free for me to call in ten minutes or so?
Yes! I'm at work so if I don't pick up I will call you right back. I often don't get reception in the basement where my office is.
Let me know when you're ready. Rooroo
Roo roo roo roo = I love you!!
Mrow meow mrow ...I love you, and how
Hey cutie pie!
Roo roo roo? (Any updates on your ❤?
It's busted
Can we do anything for you?
Perhaps a play with Rysie Piesie in the leading role?
Seriously, is there anything you want?
That just comes thru as a square.....it was probably something cute like a kitten being flusher
Flushed
I had a very intense and good dream about you while I've been away
He's retired
Damn the make a wish foundation for not giving you an iPhone!
Poor Ryan.
Will you please tell me the dream?
No.....I'm fine .....just your love! :-)
All they gave me was a bottle cap for gua sha
$75 for that bottlecap. A steal. Was it recycled from my root beer? Roo roo!
You may be too young and innocent to hear about it....
No a bleach bottle in case there's a blood spill
Tell me anyways please!
:-) :-) I'll tell you when I see you.....but it was good and reinforces there being a reason to be in each other's lives.....I have to go back in now fo
What a tease you are. Please tell me. I really want to hear. Take a walk with me on Wednesday for a minute?
r another test. Should I text later?
Yes text me always! I love texts.
Yes.....a walk would be nice.....it really is a long dream....but I'll tell you.. okay ....I'll text after the next round of tests!
Good luck in there. I do really want to hear. I was not able to remember my dreams for awhile, and I'm just now getting them back.
Roo?
Got an A in Les Rolf. Not sure how exactly!
Roo roo roo-di-doo
￼This is the Keith dress.
Beautiful!
I tried to answer but it went dead.....my signal sucks:'(
Aw
Ha
I am an endless optimist. I tried to call you one more time...
I could see why the dress could lead to a Janet Jackson moment....with your D boobs and all
Haha or ha!
Both ha and haha!
I tried to answer ..:'(
I know! Any more news?
I got an A from les too....happy to be done that semester ....
No.....I'll get results tomorrow ....
Yes me too! I really don't think I deserved an A in there.
Will you let me know? Are you at home now?
I bet the dress looks great on you.....depending on the level of fur on your legs etc
No, im in new york honey
Our tub is broken again so I'm regrowing my leg hair. I hate showering!
Almost to the monastery
Oh no......I was just getting frisky and then.......fur and menstrual cups
Good. Enjoy your time there!
My body has always been broken in some ways, for a long time, so fur and menstrual blood don't phase me.
How can you hate showering? Its just five minutes with water hitting you....
I probably couldn't explain it to you.
They phase me! Lol
The dress does look great on me. I will wear it for you someday.
We'll just let that be one of the mysteries between us.
That's a deal :-) roo
I know they phase you! I've had so much surgery and blood that leg hair is the least of my worries!
There are many mysteries indeed!
Roo roo!
I'm glad I know you!
I missed you during the break....
Me too. I can't wait to hear your dream. I need some dream time.
Take me to lunch please!
Tomorrow for sure....
For dream time ....but lunch is a date too
Do you mean Weds when we are at school? Want to have lunch then and talk?
I want to talk about nice things too when we have lunch. 30 minute moratorium on school talk.
Im not sure I'll be there Wednesday .....depending on what's happening here ....
Moratorium is good ....:-) :-) :-)
Oh got it. Tell me when you're ready to do dream time. I could use a little boost.
(I'm assuming I'm beautiful and clever in the dream.) haha
I will......losing signal ....
Ok be careful on the road.
You were beautiful, clever AND sexy! :-)
Not surprising! :)
I need a boyfriend.
Don't forget the dream.
I won't forget.... I'll text you when I come back out in the morning
Perfect. I can't wait. Though I want to hear you telling me about it too if you don't mind. I'm greedy/indulgent. Be well tonight!
You too! :-) nighty night
Goodnight Keithers.
Don't leave anything out. xoxo till morning
Good morning sweet Keith!
Hey pretty girl! :-)
I'm such a wiener! Tried to call ya right away. How much would it cost to get you a portable cell phone tower? I bet they make those...... :)
No! Moronica
Keithonica
I don't think keithonica works! :-) :-)
We gotta get you a nickname other than ers.
Any test results back?
Actually I kinda liked my nickname at my old job....given me by crazy people who would call for legal advice
What is it?
About yo lose signal.....came out for a test and I'm here...I'll text in about an hour and a half if that's good....
Yes that's great!
Hellloooooooo!
Hi!
How are you? I have a few minutes before I ak back at the monastery and no longer have a signal and thought I would say Hellloooooooo
Yah!
I am well. I had a really nice acupuncture appt with Bob today. I am so glad to have him.
Ed emailed us our clinical requirements manual and I started reading it and got really nervous about all the rules and hours etc
Did he have bracelets for earings?
Glad I don't have wifi! :-)
I know there will end up being the manual on one hand and reality on another. Otherwise how will Zac or Mike ever make it through?
Yes glad you don't have wifi.
No earrings but cute jokes. :) Are you coming for orientation? I guess not.
How do the m
Oops
Btw......do you have a copy of the fall semester's clinic log.....Mary Ellen had my whole book .....I never got it back and Janet emailed me so I have to
recreate the log :'( :'( I don't know who came when
How do the monks tweet without wifi? Dhich Nhat Hahn has quite a following.
I must have it. This past fall? I will look.
He sends love notes to his nun mistress and she emails for him....it's a labor of love
That would be so incredibly sweet!
Yup...i never missed an observation .....
He sends her peanut butter cups too
I'm not sure about tomorrow ....I should decide soon tho! Lol
I want to say both: Come back to me!!! AND: Stay there!!!
True romance. Peanut butter cups!
That's how Rogers and Hammerstein pictured true love!
Close up of a pb cup?
You know who they are right? Or is that just my era?
Yes I know who they are!
Good! I thought do....you've known enough men without flannel shirts, so......
Haha
I wish I could see those men without their flannels on...oh wait, I can!!!---on Kevin's Instagram feed! Haha. All of his friends are hot gay men he has never met. It's kind if cliche.
When do I get my dream?
Oh lord, monicers.......no no no! Drooling over gay men is like salivating over wax fruit! I have so much to teach you!!!! :-) :-) :-)
I'm actually repulsed by that much waxed up muscle mass. No worries. (Though that alone may worry you.)
Ok....I better stop bulking phase! Haha
I like your muscles!
I have muscles? Do you know who you're texting? :-)
What! You're all muscle!
When do I get my dream? :)
You said you wanna hear it and I don't have a strong enough signal to call I think..I can't make a call go thru..try calling me ....
Nope! Won't work?
Hmm!
That's: won't work.
Same here
T-mobile sucks!
No way you'll get a signal, right?
Not in this area ......
I want to talk! But there's no way to do that....
Soon, honey
Ok
I'm being pouty. Texting is not nearly as good.
Metal
PS: when you see me, I'm gonna have a giant bruise on the left side of my jaw. Bob underestimated the fact that I have no fat in that side of my face. My sweet side.
Should we sue, lawyer dad?
Wood
Not really Wood, I don't know. It's just nice to connect with actual voices, or in person.
Getting frustrated? Wanna go....?
Yes.....Bob's going down ......
Wanna go what?
I like Bob though! But my face is all banged up. Poor left side has a hard time being touched.
We're getting his needles, cotton balls (literally) and autoclave
Awesome.
What did he do?
I need new cotton balls. Foolishly shared with the class, including Mike, who never shares anything, before CNT.
Stomach 5
Ooh! Almost back to cell service you mean?
Almost back to my cell.....
Ummmmmm......Bob actually has cotton balls
Isn't stomach 5 on your stomach?
No....to no service :-(
Ah! No service at all!!! :( Pouty kitty face. Like when you serve a kitty the wrong flavor of canned meat.
I didn't name the point previously bc I was counting on you not knowing where it is. :)
Bob is the best.
He didn't mean to bruise me.
I'm loyal. By choice and by conviction.
Like spam! Roo roo
You are correct sir!
Ummmmm.....because he heals what ails you or his bedside manner? I suspect.......
Both. Mostly I love who he is. Absolutely nothing was wrong with me today. Nothing at all.
Roo roo
I must be doing ok if someone's having dreams where I'm sexy and smart.
If he had ed's personality but stuck the same point, would you say he's the best?

No never. And I know I'm bolstering your argument right now but I'm being honest. I can't heal comfortably with people I don't like. My dentist of 10 years was a jerk and I think his ego impacted our treatments. He took it too far.
You know how I feel.....we have the luxury of just looking at minimal gradations of "eyes look brighter " or "more shen! "....but if my child had sepsis
and was writhing in pain.....I'd want healing not stroking....and I know you would too
You are sexy and smart!!! :-) :-)
I know. That's true.
Thanks Keith. :)
Maybe acupuncture is meant to aid, not cure.
So when I get my children's hospice .....I want to help with pain and illness.....not be sweet ......sweet's good, talented and expert's better ....sweet
, talented and expert is best I think
Oh Keith, you will do great.
You will find your way I think.
Like your back......an acupuncturist may have been all sweet and nice to you.....but you wanted relief
It's true.
But pain is the one thing Acu seems to help?
So.....OUR goal.....mine and yours .....should be know what we're doing and help our patient enjoy the process.....otherwise just take Dr Phil home study
My dad makes Dr Phil's chili every time I come home. Haha
DVDs and don't bother with three years of this crap....:-) :-) :-)
Yes pain seems to be on the radar of things we can reliably say THIS medicine works with! There ya go Ryan! A concession!....Lol
Ah! It's killing me that I can't call.
Oh Ryan.
Can you just pull over underneath a giant cell tower?
In a giant chili pot I bet
Ok....I better go in before lights out! For sure I'll make sure we talk tomorrow! I love you!

I'm feeling nervous about tomorrow. Clinic and rules and gruff Ed and I'm afraid he will be pissed I'm missing 4 shifts for Laura. I do plan to make them all up. There's some weird thing about attendance I don't understand.
My dad is adorable.
Goodnight.
Bring me more good dreams please?
Please be well tonight. And rest? :*
Btw.....at my law job for ten years....lots of crazies that called for advice couldn't get my name right ....and would ask for O'Malley.. in the end the
entire federal agency would always refer to me as simply O'Malley....even my boss. They had t shirts made one year that said O'Malley on the back for eve
rybody in Harrisburg, Pittsburgh and Philly
Nighty night!!!! Sweet dreams!
You're sweet.
What's so hard about LaValley? :) :) xoxo
